"snippet" : "Clearance plane (1): all vertical retract and stepdown movements to the next machining plane take place via the clearance plane. Clearance distance \/ Lead-in position (2) The stepdown movement to the next workplane is realized with Contour Milling at the clearance distance (A), with Pocket Milling a...", 
