"breadcrumbs" : "CAM \/ 3D Machining \/ Optimized Rest Machining \/ Strategy \/ Blending ", 
"snippet" : "Smooth overlap : Smooth overlapping of the toolpaths between different machining areas ensures a very high surface quality in the area of transition from the surfaces of the vertical corners to the laterally adjacent surfaces. If the option is enabled, additional toolpaths (B) are added to the stand...", 
