"snippet" : "Rotary axes \/ Tool axis You can define the display, color and length for the machine elements rotary axes, tool axis and reference point for the machines that are used in the simulation. Increments Length and angle by which the machine axes can be moved. Origin name scheme In addition to the prefix ...", 
