"snippet" : "I have bought a license for the OPEN MIND direct interfaces, but the toolbar for the interfaces is not available. Check on the Activation code tab of your OPEN MIND License Manager whether you have activated the direct interfaces for your dongle. Please find information on activation in the Activate...", 
